**Реализация**:
- `apps/server/prisma/schema.prisma` + миграция
  `20260703183300_user_xp_desc_index` — индекс `User_xp_idx`
  на `xp DESC` для быстрого leaderboard.
- `packages/shared/src/schemas/leaderboard.ts` — `LeaderboardQuerySchema`
  (period: week|all, limit: 1-100), `LeaderboardEntrySchema`
  (rank, userId, displayName, xp, currentStreak, isCurrentUser)
